<br>
EQ is based off of old MUDS and they added all the annoying factors like binding, massive downtime, camps, etc., Camelot is built under a different philosophy in that its a game and should be enjoyable, not feel like a job.<br>
<br>
Besides, the way I see it, if I played camelot first, then EQ came out and I wanted to try it and had to put up with spending an hour looking for a bind, losing my corpse, screwed up tradeskills, massive exp loss for death, fighting over spawns, possibility of endless hours looking for a group in order to do anything, needing to dedicate a 4-5 hour period of time once I get into a group...I would never try EQ.<br>
<br>
UO is a waste since 'Lord British' left...I will never buy another Ultima based game again. Beta tested AC for awhile, I still think thats the worst online game out there with the exception of AO where you pay 10 bucks a month to play a single player game with no content.<br>
<br>
